import Title from "./component/Title"
import {Navbar, Nav, Button} from "react-bootstrap"
import {FloatingLabelsSearch} from '@components/forms/index.js'

const SubNavbar = (props) => {

    return  <>

            <Navbar  bg="primary" variant="dark" className="mt-5 w-50 mx-auto">

            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">
                <Title></Title>
            </Navbar.Brand>

            <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">

            <FloatingLabelsSearch handleChange={props.handleChange} val={props.valSerach} />

            <Nav className="ms-auto">

                <Nav.Link href="/profile">
                    <Button type="button" className="btn btn-light btn-md ">Find Matches</Button>
                </Nav.Link>

            </Nav>

            </Navbar.Collapse>

            </Navbar>

            </>
 }

 export default SubNavbar
